    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total showstopper? I\u2019m parting with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014not a scratch, no weird smells, and it drives like a dream. I've taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. You really won\u2019t find one in better shape than this. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3, a definitive example of the final naturally aspirated V8 M-car. This specimen features the high-revving 4.0L S65 engine, delivering 414 hp through eight individual throttle bodies to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain is complemented by a functional M-Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. This 'mint' unit has undergone meticulous mechanical vetting, including preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, and the factory Alpine White finish is devoid of any swirling or imperfections. An analog masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless exterior. Pristine interior. Full service history. No mechanical issues. Title in hand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since its first mile. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, recently protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, it has been fastidiously maintained with a fully documented service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this car offers an uncompromising ownership experience. All original keys, manuals, and service receipts are included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are honored to present this vehicle, an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This unit remains in pristine condition, showcasing a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original showroom luster. Every detail has been meticulously curated to satisfy the most exacting requirements of a discerning buyer. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defines the pinnacle of its class, offering both mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already addressed. A meticulously maintained VANOS system ensures optimal variable valve timing across the rev range. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue, the paint depth is consistent with factory standards, showing zero oxidation. The interior retains its original Nappa leather integrity and factory tactile response. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
